{"html": [{"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&#xA0;</div></div>", "i": 8331702}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Por resoluci&#xF3;n N&#xBA; 931, de 30 de junio de 1998, de esta Subsecretar&#xED;a de Pesca, del Ministerio de Econom&#xED;a, Fomento y Reconstrucci&#xF3;n, modif&#xED;case el numeral 1&#xBA; de la resoluci&#xF3;n N&#xBA; 763, de 1995, que autoriz&#xF3; a PESQUERA SAN JOSE S.A., para desarrollar actividades pesqueras extractivas con la nave &apos;&apos;Don Julio&apos;&apos;, en el sentido de actualizar las caracter&#xED;sticas n&#xE1;uticas de esta &#xFA;ltima, en los t&#xE9;rminos que se indica:</div><div class=\"p\"> </div><div class=\"p\">Matr&#xED;cula&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2870</div><div class=\"p\">Eslora de Arqueo&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  58,9&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; m</div><div class=\"p\">T.R.G. (Internacional)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  1397</div><div class=\"p\">Capacidad de Bodega&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1610,0&nbsp; &nbsp; m3</div><div class=\"p\">Potencia Motor Principal&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  4398&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Hp</div><div class=\"p\">Potencia Motor Auxiliar&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1073&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Hp</div><div class=\"p\">Arte de Pesca&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Cerco y arrastre de media agua.</div><br></div>", "i": 8331703}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Valpara&#xED;so, 30 de junio de 1998.- Juan Manuel Cruz S&#xE1;nchez, Subsecretario de Pesca.</div><br></div>", "i": 8331704}], "proyectos": [], "otrosSistemas": [], "jurisprudencia": [], "doctrina": [], "metadatos": {"tiene_notas": false, "tipos_numeros": [{"tipo": "3", "numero": "931", "abreviacion": "RES", "desc